 <text>
  <front>
   <head>[From the same Opera.]</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">When gentle whispers of a prosp'rous gale</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Direct the sailor to the much-lov'd shore,</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">To court the breeze he hoists the swelling sail,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">With hope elate he plies the lab'ring oar.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">When strait the treach'rous winds are taught to roar,</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">The angry waves obey the harsh command;</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">With stupid grief he views the less'ning shore,</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">And vainly strives to reach the distant land.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Thus cruel fate, inconstant as the air,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Just shews me joys, that ah! I ne'er must taste;</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">And when I stretch my arms to grasp the fair,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">She snatches from me the inviting feast.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
